Package: heartFailurePredict
Title: Heart Disease Diagnosis Prediction Tool
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given="Zijie.Lu", family="Lu", role=c("aut","cre"), email="3058317394@qq.com")
Description: A user-friendly R package to predict heart disease diagnosis based on clinical features (e.g., Age, ChestPainType). Trained on heart.csv dataset with random forest model, supporting fast prediction for both batch and single samples.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/Lubio215/heartFailurePredict
